	From Hisazumi Kenji <nel@soraneko.com>:
	* stage2/fsys_ffs.c (mapblock_offset): New variable.
	(mapblock_bsize): Likewise.
	(MAPBUF): New macro.
	(MAPBUF_LEN): Likewise.
	(ffs_mount): Set MAPBLOCK_OFFSET to -1.
	(block_map): Added partial read support.

